snippet.title: Wéko The Mask Gatherer – Release Date Trailer - Steam
snippet.description:
Wéko The Mask Gatherer is coming to Steam on July 26th!  

Embark on an enchanting adventure in Wéko The Mask Gatherer, the debut game from indie developer SIRO GAMES! Navigate through a vibrant world filled with exploration, combat, and puzzles, using mystical masks to unlock special abilities and uncover secrets.

#WekoTheMaskGatherer #Steam

Visit our Steam page for all the latest! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1682290/Wko_The_Mask_Gatherer/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Wekoproject
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wekoproject/
Discord: Join our community https://discord.gg/Jev94JjjsR
